The final ever episode of Doomlord sees Enok destroyed whilst fighting the Moraqi Superman (who is being controlled by alien parasites). Enok's brother still lives (although a ghoulish vampire with a taste for human blood) - the final panel sees him restling with the choice of whether to protect humanity or destroy it.

The Friendly Ghost makes his return to comics at last, and he's bringing his Scare School with him! It's Halloween in Deedstown, and Casper and the Gang make plans to go trick-or-treating - after all, it's the one day of the year that they can get together in public without raising much suspicion! But when Wolfie goes candy-crazy, can Casper calm him down before the 'fleshies' take notice?
name: Halloween Is for the Dogs

Plus: art cut from the DVD documentary film on Mack's work, The Alchemy of Art: David Mack, from Herovideoproductions.com.

description: In the late 1970s Brain Bolland left an indelible mark on the minds of many comic fans with his stunningly orginal, often controversial work on 2000AD's Judge Dredd. He went on to attract an even bigger audience with Camelot 3000 and Batman:The Killing Joke and remains a popular and much sought-after cover artist. This collection of short strips, on which Bolland is sole author, takes you away from the the guns and testosterone and into a world of wit and whimsy exclusively his own. The Actress and The Bishop stories take up the first half of the book, followed by the single page Mr. Mamoulian strips Bolland's alter ego taking a wry philosophical and very funny look at the world. The book is completed with assorted strips ranging from Fairy Tales to serious historical travelogue and some full page illustrations.
name: Bolland Strips!

description: An eclectic and stylish collection of comics from Rian Hughes, renowned illustrator and designer in a luxury embossed hardcover. All the stories here have been recoloured or relettered to show them at their best. Long before he discovered the Apple Mac, Hughes was collaborating with Eisner Award-winner Grant Morrison on the classic British character Dan Dare, producing a post-modern classic which sets an ageing, retired Dare against a modern British landscape he no longer understands. Versatile and unpredictable, Hughes makes full use of his clean graphic style on The Science Service, written by John Freeman, and a looser, moody noir palette on Raymond Chandler's Goldfish, here adapted by writer Tom DeHaven. Really & Truly, another Morrison collaboration, is a high-octane psychedelic road-trip torn from the pages of cult comic 2000AD. As well as sketchbook pages, merchandise and rare strips - many never seen before or out of print for over a decade - the book features an introduction by comics guru Paul Gravett.
name: TPB

description: The scientist's name is Hank Pym. The socialite's is Janet Van Dyne. Both are haunted by personal tragedy and the burning need to...avenge! It's insect love, Marvel-style, as we revisit the unlikely origin (and courtship) of the astonishing Ant-Man and the winsome Wasp!
name: Avengers Origns: Ant-Man and The Wasp

description: Natasha Romanov has always led an exciting life - first as a Cold War-era Soviet spy, followed by her defection to the West. She has earned a reputation through the years as a consummate professional, coldly efficient and as deadly as her namesake. Now, her time as Black Widow may be at an end. Yelena Belova, the new Black Widow, seeks to claim the mantle she feels was stolen from her Motherland. Trained in the arts of espionage and combat, and anxious to prove herself and eliminate her counterpart, Belova will stop at nothing to achieve her goal. The battle of the two Widows rages from the deserts of the Middle East to New York's Upper West Side. When the smoke clears, will either be left standing? Collecting BLACK WIDOW (1999) #1-3 and BLACK WIDOW (2001) #1-3.
name: HC

description: No longer able to abide Professor X's passive ideals, the young members of X-Force split from the X-Men to carve out their own aggressive destiny! Featuring the threats of Magneto, the X-Ternals and...War Machine!? Guest-starring Deadpool, Nick Fury, the New Warriors, Storm and Beast - and featuring the return of Cable! Collecting NEW WARRIORS (1990) #31 and X-FORCE (1991) #19-25.
name: HC

description: An alien army attacks NoMan, after strikes on Moscow and the USS Columbia space shuttle. The Soviets blame the United States, and gives them forty-eight hours to prove their innocence. Meanwhile, Lightning struggles with his feelings for Kitten and tells her that field agents shouldn't see each other. She tells him to get lost. The Raven busies himself by taking out some drug-dealers, and the T.H.U.N.D.E.R. Squad stops a ship's drug cargo from being picked up. Dynamite decides to blow up the storage unit where the junk is waiting, but they get trapped in the room when the alarm sets off fumes of knock-out gas. Lightning swoops in for a speedy rescue. Meanwhile, NoMan is finally able to switch to another android body in T.H.U.N.D.E.R. Control, but needs to recover his cape which was left behind. However, he is told that Dynamo is already on the job. Unfortunately, he is ambushed by a goon squad during his search, but they are no match for him, and his foes easily fall. He then hears a familiar voice, turns around, and finds the Iron Maiden!
name: The Invasion Begins!

description: Featuring No-Man, Dynamo, and the other classic Tower heroes.
name: Battle In D.C.!

description: The new, improved Doomsday is back in these tales from STEEL #1, OUTSIDERS #37, JUSTICE LEAGUE OF AMERICA #55, SUPERMAN/ BATMAN ANNUAL #5 and SUPERBOY #6!
name: TPB

description:
A new hardcover starring Astro City's most popular heroes, collecting ASTRO CITY: ASTRA #1-2, ASTRO CITY: SILVER AGENT #1-2, ASTRO CITY: SAMARITAN and ASTRO CITY: BEAUTIE #1.

Astra Furst, a third-generation super hero of Astro City, is graduating from college. It's a time of friends and family, new opportunities, changing relationships – and danger! Featuring the First Family, the creatures of Monstro City, a new hero team and more on a graduation night nobody's ever going to forget!

Also in this volume: at last, the full story of the Silver Agent's fateful journey through time is revealed – including his origin, his greatest battles and his ultimate fate. Plus, Beautie, the life-size super-powered fashion-doll member of Honor Guard, doesn't know who she is. Now, she's determined to get answers.
name: HC/TPB

description: After witnessing the demise of most of her StormWatch teammates, Jenny Sparks wants to create a new super hero team dedicated to protecting Earth against threats of a global scale. Joined by former StormWatch members Jack Hawksmoor and Shen Li-Min, Jenny recruits four new members, the Doctor, the Engineer, Apollo, and the Midnighter forming the ultra-powerful Authority. Collected in this edition are their first two missions, battling a nation of super-powered terrorists and stopping an invasion from a parallel world.
name: TPB

description: A new collection featuring the first 6 issues of the explosive maxiseries! The Authority has settled into its role as governing body of the U.S. But with many unhappy Americans and a powerful foe working behind-the-scenes, can a second American Revolution be far behind?
name: Book 1

first_appearance_teams.name: Paul Revere and the Sons of Liberty

team_credits.name: Paul Revere and the Sons of Liberty

description: Collecting the final six issues of this amazing Authority tale! After the debacle in the nation's capital that led to the total destruction of Washington, DC, the Authority relinquished control of the United States and all but vanished. How long can tyranny stand, before heroes will rise up?
name: Book 2

description: The Authority's struggle to change the world takes on a new chapter in this trade paperback collecting issues #6-10! The Authority have assumed control of the government of the US! But it won't be an easy road, as the American people aren't all for it!
name: Vol. 6

description: Collecting the red-hot 6-issue miniseries! The Authority and StormWatch Prime were once teammates and the closest of comrades…but a custody battle over Henry Bendix's secret bunker causes long-held grudges to boil over! It's mayhem as two of the strongest teams in the WildStorm Universe collide in a battle for the ages!
name: TPB

description: The super-team created to protect Earth from threats of a global scale struggle to carry on after they fail in their mission. In this collection featuring issues #8–17 of their monthly series, find out what The Authority must do after their world is destroyed.
name: Book 2

description: Collecting the thrilling 6-issue NINJA BOY miniseries! When his family is brutally slain by the evil warlord Mikaboshi, young Nakio — last survivor of the Mugen Ninja Clan — sets upon a path of vengeance! The Ninja Boy, and the friends he makes along the way, must find the wizard Jurojin — the one person with the power to stop Mikaboshi — or fall victim to the dark lord's elite assassins.
name: TPB

description: Collecting the first five issues of the WildStorm series based on the international anime sensation following the adventures of wandering Ronin Jubei, as he scours feudal Japan while fighting all forms of villains and monsters!
name: TPB

description: An ancient evil from another dimension named Draedalus has deceptively begun to take over El Dorado City by promising its citizens a better life in return for their services and allegiance. But when four teens begin to develop extraordinary psychic powers, they alone realize the true danger of this "deal with the devil." Now with demons infesting their town and the city's population against them, a high school outcast, a nerdy bookworm, a star quarterback and a prom queen must find a way to put aside their own differences and save their family and friends from impending doom.
name: TPB

description: ORION THE GATES OF APOKOLIPS: is a fast-paced tale about a never-ending battle between a father and son with the fate of the universe in the balance. Raised from birth to be a warrior, Orion has spent a lifetime opposing his father, the maniacal godlike Darkseid. But when the evil despot discovers the secret to ultimate power, the scales are tipped and the brutal and ruthless anti-hero must find a way to bring down his father or watch as the malicious tyrant takes over the entire universe.
name: TPB

description: Novelist Kevin J. Anderson's popular science fiction series comes to comics as an original hardcover graphic novel! THE SAGA OF SEVEN SUNS: VEILED ALLIANCES, is a complex and vast story told on a cosmic scale. As the human race expands into the stars, they find themselves caught up in the politics and long-standing feuds of several powerful alien races. It's a tale of galactic empire building, filled with political and familial intrigue, love and war, and a host of alien lifeforms, all competing to be the supreme force in the universe!
name: TPB/HC

volume.name: The Saga of Seven Suns: Veiled Alliances

description: Collecting the entire 6-issue miniseries, this is the story of The Authority's urban hero Jack Hawksmoor before he joined the team. While preventing a massive robot attack on the Golden Gate Bridge, Hawksmoor gets unexpected assistance from a mysterious woman, then stumbles upon a locked-room murder mystery.
name: TPB

volume.name: The Secret History of the Authority: Hawksmoor

description: Renowned comics icon Joe Kubert returns to the legendary military unit he made famous in this action-packed tale based on a true story! Collecting the acclaimed 6-issue miniseries, this volume has Rock and his company of hard-bitten veterans in the No Man's Land of the Balkans searching for a religious prize that could decide the outcome of World War II!
name: TPB

description: Sgt. Rock returns in this new tale inspired by true events. From the bloody beaches of Normandy to the muddy forests of the Vosges Mountains, Easy Company is joined by Johnny Cloud, the Haunted Tank and other DC war heroes as they battle for their lives behind enemy lines against a force ten times their size. From the six-issue miniseries.
name: TPB/HC
